'''水牛城野牛'''（{{lang-en|Buffalo Bisons}}），是[[美國職棒小聯盟|美國職棒小聯盟]]的球隊，目前隸屬於[[多倫多藍鳥|多倫多藍鳥]]的[[3A等級|3A體系]]。球隊主場位於[[紐約州|紐約州]][[水牛城|水牛城]]的[[薩倫球場|薩倫球場]]，這座球場也是目前3A球隊中，容客量最多的一座球場。

這支球隊於1979年成立，並沿用以前曾在水牛城的小聯盟球隊的隊名野牛做為球隊的新名稱。1991年，他們在這年一共賣出124萬又951張票，寫下了小聯盟球隊的單季售票紀錄。富比士在2016年將野牛隊評為小聯盟最有錢球隊中的第15名。<ref>{{cite web|last=Klebnikov|first=Sergei|url=https://www.forbes.com/pictures/gkle45ffh/15-buffalo-bisons/#449d56912efa|title=Minor League Baseball's Most Valuable Teams – 15. Buffalo Bisons|website=Forbes|date=July 8, 2016|access-date=September 23, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127041328/https://www.forbes.com/pictures/gkle45ffh/15-buffalo-bisons/#449d56912efa|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==球隊歷史==
[[File:War_Memorial_Stadium_Rockpile.JPG|thumb]]
1978年，水牛城市長[[詹姆斯·D·格里芬|詹姆斯·D·格里芬]]（James D. Griffin）買下了[[奧克蘭運動家|奧克蘭運動家]]的2A球隊—澤西市運動家的股權，並將這支球隊改組更名為水牛城野牛。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Moritz |first1=Amy |title=Buffalo's downtown ballpark: The house that Jimmy built |url=https://buffalonews.com/sports/baseball/professional/buffalos-downtown-ballpark-the-house-that-jimmy-built/article_d0fa6e07-40ef-58ae-9a54-19a1a5db0a2c.html |work=The Buffalo News |date=July 14, 2017}}</ref>1979年至1984年，野牛隊都在[[東方聯盟|東方聯盟]]出賽。1983年，水牛城富豪[[小羅伯特·E·里奇|小羅伯特·E·里奇]]（Robert E. Rich Jr.）以10萬美元買下野牛隊，<ref>{{Cite web|title=After 20 years, Bisons still a hit for Bob Rich Jr.|url=https://www.bizjournals.com/buffalo/stories/2003/03/31/story4.html|access-date=2021-03-09|website=www.bizjournals.com|archive-date=2006-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060629034433/http://www.bizjournals.com/buffalo/stories/2003/03/31/story4.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>並讓他們在1985年升格成為3A球隊。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1988-09-06-sp-1717-story.html|title=A Major League Effort for Buffalo|date=September 6, 1988|website=Los Angeles Times}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.newspapers.com/newspage/451794970/|title=The Daily Oklahoman from Oklahoma City, Oklahoma on September 8, 1984 · 72|website=Newspapers.com}}</ref>

1988年，球隊的主場移到了飛行員球場，也就是現今的薩倫球場。那年一共有118萬6651人進場觀看比賽，刷新了小聯盟球隊單年觀眾數紀錄。<ref>{{cite news|title=Buffalo Bisons Set Minor League Attendance Mark|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1988-08-20/sports/sp-568_1_minor-league|newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=August 20, 1988|access-date=May 15, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517132448/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-08-20/sports/sp-568_1_minor-league|archive-date=May 17, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Buffalo Bisons Franchise History (1878-2019) |url=https://www.statscrew.com/minorbaseball/t-bb10631 |website=statscrew.com |access-date=2021-03-22 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027090349/https://www.statscrew.com/minorbaseball/t-bb10631 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1991年，野牛隊更將紀錄推高到124萬951人次。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://milb.bamcontent.com/documents/1/4/2/308944142/2019_Buffalo_Bisons_Media_Guide.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-22 |archive-date=2020-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719024647/https://milb.bamcontent.com/documents/1/4/2/308944142/2019_Buffalo_Bisons_Media_Guide.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>而球隊也在1991年和1992年拿下分區冠軍。

1995年，[[克里夫蘭印地安人|印地安人隊]]接替了[[匹茲堡海盜|海盜隊]]成為野牛隊的大聯盟附屬球隊。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://buffalonews.com/news/simply-the-best-the-bisons-have-established-a-winning-tradition-since-hooking-up-with-the/article_84def3c7-f095-5c51-901e-22d03443b0f7.html|title='SIMPLY THE BEST' THE BISONS HAVE ESTABLISHED A WINNING TRADITION SINCE HOOKING UP WITH THE CLEVELAND INDIANS IN 1995|first=Mike|last=Harrington|website=The Buffalo News}}</ref>之後更是6年內拿下5次分區冠軍。1997年6月20日，[[巴特羅·柯隆|巴特羅·柯隆]]投出了隊史第一場的無安打比賽。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/cut4/a-trip-back-to-bartolo-colon-s-first-and-only-no-hitter-c281758064 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-22 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129074836/https://www.mlb.com/cut4/a-trip-back-to-bartolo-colon-s-first-and-only-no-hitter-c281758064 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1998年，球隊曾成功闖進3A的世界大賽，不過最終輸球無緣拿下冠軍。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.milb.com/news/gcs-166827450|title=Triple-A still thriving after 1998 realignment|website=MiLB.com}}</ref>後來球隊在2000年代又拿下了4次分區冠軍，其中2004年更是成為聯盟冠軍。

2009年，野牛隊成為[[大都會隊|大都會隊]]的附屬小聯盟球隊。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:4ozuiT7ywdkJ:https://www.bizjournals.com/buffalo/stories/2008/09/22/daily7.html+&cd=8&hl=en&ct=clnk&gl=us|title=Bisons meet the Mets - Buffalo Business First|website=webcache.googleusercontent.com}}</ref>不過這段期間，觀眾的入場數下滑很多。

2013年，野牛隊變成了藍鳥隊的附屬3A球隊。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/8409223/triple-buffalo-bisons-switch-affiliation-toronto-blue-jays|title=Triple-A Buffalo switches affiliation to Blue Jays|date=September 22, 2012|website=ESPN.com}}</ref>同年4月18日，球隊曾單場敲出29支安打拿下27分，寫下小聯盟單場得分紀錄。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130418&content_id=45145478&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_t422&sid=t422 | title=RECORDS fall in 27–9 Bisons win – Unforgettable team performance as Buffalo earns sweep | publisher=Buffalo Bisons | date=April 18, 2013 | access-date=April 20, 2013 | author=Bisbing, Brad | archive-date=2016-03-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160327051934/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130418&content_id=45145478&vkey=news_t422&fext=.jsp&sid=t422 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130418&content_id=45153940&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb | title=Negrych cycles in Bisons' record rout | publisher=MLB.com | date=April 18, 2013 | access-date=April 20, 2013 | author=Parker, John | archive-date=2016-09-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914093008/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130418&content_id=45153940&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb | dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年，因為[[COVID-19疫情|COVID-19疫情]]關係，加上小聯盟賽事取消，野牛隊將主場薩倫球場借給藍鳥隊做為賽季主場。

由於[[國際聯盟_(棒球)|國際聯盟]]在2021年不敵疫情關閉，裡面所有球隊全數併入小聯盟組成了[[3A東區|3A東區]]，其中包含了野牛隊。<ref name=JMayo2-12-2021>{{cite web|last=Mayo|first=Jonathan|title=MLB Announces New Minors Teams, Leagues|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/new-minor-league-baseball-structure|website=Major League Baseball|date=February 12, 2021|access-date=February 12, 2021|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306212148/https://www.mlb.com/news/new-minor-league-baseball-structure|dead-url=no}}</ref>

